description:
Happy Halloween everyone! What better way to celebrate Halloween than with a spooky tale? :) I asked Knuckles, who's a good friend of mine, to write me a really scary story for my halloween special and he was more than happy to do so!(he actually said no at first because he told me he would be busy around halloween, but after I told him he would be telling the story himself in the video he immediately agreed lol)

Anyway, please comment, rate, subscribe, and if you want to, send me all your halloween candy in the mail. If you do that, i'll try to convince sonic and Bartleby of letting me film them as Bartleby shoves the candy up Sonic's ass. ;) 

I know how much you guys would love to see that lol.
creator: Charice
